name: offboard heartbeat
Start sending the offboard heartbeat message so we can arm in offboard mode
set current heading
func:
let current_heading = msg.payload.heading
msg.payload = Math.round(current_heading * 100) / 100
flow.set("current_heading", current_heading)
return msg
